WEBVTT

01:47.691 --> 01:49.401
<b>Who are you?</b>

01:49.401 --> 01:51.031
<b>U-Uh...</b>

01:51.031 --> 01:53.531
<b>My name is Sasaki.</b>

01:53.531 --> 01:56.281
<b>Yeah? Sasaki-san?</b>

01:56.911 --> 01:59.451
<b>You're trespassing. I'm reporting you.</b>

02:01.751 --> 02:05.671
<b>P-Please wait one moment! 
I'm a friend of Tayama-san's!</b>

02:05.671 --> 02:10.171
<b>She invited me to smoke here when I was 
walking around looking for a smoking area.</b>

02:10.171 --> 02:14.551
<b>I've been taking her up 
on her offer ever since...</b>

02:15.591 --> 02:17.221
<b></b>puff

02:15.891 --> 02:16.841
<b>Eek!</b>

02:17.851 --> 02:19.811
<b><i>Who the heck is "Tayama"?</i></b>

02:20.431 --> 02:23.061
<b><i>Wait, now that I look at him,</i></b>

02:23.061 --> 02:27.811
<b><i>he's that gaffer who always lines up 
at Yamada's register with a smile.</i></b>

02:28.441 --> 02:33.441
<b></b>Pet Dog

02:28.441 --> 02:33.441
<b>Beth</b>

02:28.691 --> 02:32.321
<b><i>I recognize him because he resembles 
my family dog, but...</i></b>

02:32.321 --> 02:33.441
<b>"Tayama"?</b>

02:33.861 --> 02:35.651
<b>Don't you mean Yamada?</b>

02:35.651 --> 02:38.951
<b>Wh-Why would you bring Yamada-san up?</b>

02:39.871 --> 02:41.791
<b>No, I mean Tayama-san!</b>

02:41.791 --> 02:44.871
<b>The responsible girl 
wearing that cool, flashy jacket.</b>

02:45.211 --> 02:48.711
<b>She says she and Yamada-san 
are good friends.</b>

02:49.171 --> 02:53.091
<b><i>Oh, I see. This guy's getting played.</i></b>

02:59.551 --> 03:02.851
<b>So, you're here to smoke with Ya...</b>

03:02.851 --> 03:05.101
<b>Tayama again?</b>

03:05.101 --> 03:08.901
<b>Oh, no. I just had something to give her.</b>

03:08.901 --> 03:10.111
<b>A gift?</b>

03:12.191 --> 03:14.611
<b>Is she making you simp for her?</b>

03:14.611 --> 03:16.241
<b>It's a token of my appreciation!</b>

03:16.241 --> 03:17.701
<b><i>Uh-huh...</i></b>

03:21.331 --> 03:24.251
<b>Tayama should be clocking out soon.</b>

03:24.251 --> 03:26.001
<b>Do you want me to go get her?</b>

03:26.001 --> 03:28.211
<b>Oh, no, don't bother!</b>

03:28.211 --> 03:31.631
<b>I just figured I could 
hand it over if she was here.</b>

03:32.501 --> 03:37.511
<b>Sorry, could you pass this 
on to her for me?</b>

03:37.761 --> 03:40.141
<b>That should clear things up.</b>

03:44.891 --> 03:47.981
<b>I apologize for interrupting you 
during your break.</b>

03:50.771 --> 03:54.111
<b><i>He really does resemble my family dog.</i></b>

03:54.111 --> 03:55.071
<b><i>Beth...</i></b>

03:57.191 --> 03:59.071
<b>Manager.</b>

04:07.751 --> 04:10.461
<b>If you were going to smoke, 
you should've invited me.</b>

04:17.421 --> 04:20.181
<b>You're getting a talking-to, Yamada.</b>

04:20.181 --> 04:21.841
<b>Wait, why?</b>

04:22.551 --> 04:25.141
<b>You've been smoking here with 
a customer without permission.</b>

04:29.351 --> 04:30.641
<b>I would never.</b>

04:30.641 --> 04:32.191
<b>Pull the other one, Yamada!</b>

04:32.481 --> 04:35.901
<b>Don't try to lie your way out of this. 
Sasaki-kun told me about it.</b>

04:35.901 --> 04:38.571
<b>Wait, he was here?</b>

04:38.571 --> 04:40.741
<b>He just left.</b>

04:40.741 --> 04:44.121
<b>Sheesh. I nearly called the cops 
on him for trespassing.</b>

04:45.871 --> 04:47.951
<b>He said this was for "Tayama-san."</b>

04:51.871 --> 04:54.501
<b>Called it a token of his appreciation.</b>

04:54.501 --> 04:56.921
<b>You're this Tayama, right?</b>

05:00.631 --> 05:05.141
<b>Tayama and Yamada, though? 
Talk about half-assed.</b>

05:05.141 --> 05:08.311
<b>He's probably the only one that'd fool.</b>

05:08.311 --> 05:11.731
<b>You'd better not mess with that 
good-natured gaffer too much.</b>

05:11.731 --> 05:14.731
<b>Hey! Are you listening to me, Yamada...</b>

05:15.731 --> 05:18.191
<b>I told him it was no biggie...</b>

05:22.111 --> 05:25.371
<b><i>Oho, I get what's going on here.</i></b>

05:25.031 --> 05:28.241
<b>Boss Gauge</b>

05:25.031 --> 05:29.751
<b>Hint of Romance</b>

05:25.031 --> 05:29.751
<b>Hint of Romance</b>

05:25.031 --> 05:29.751
<b>Ethics</b>

05:25.031 --> 05:29.751
<b>Ethics</b>

05:30.581 --> 05:34.251
<b><i>It's the perfect entertainment 
for these monotonous night shifts.</i></b>

05:34.251 --> 05:35.581
<b><i>I'll let them be for a bit.</i></b>

05:51.731 --> 05:55.691
<b><i>I ended up making myself 
scarce last night.</i></b>

05:55.691 --> 05:58.981
<b><i>I hope Tayama-san didn't get 
chewed out because of me.</i></b>

06:00.361 --> 06:02.111
<b><i>Don't bring a gaffer in here!</i></b>

06:02.111 --> 06:04.741
<b><i>I'm sorry for bringing a gaffer in here.</i></b>

06:05.861 --> 06:07.411
<b><i>I'm confiscating this gift!</i></b>

06:07.411 --> 06:09.491
<b><i>Please, have mercy!</i></b>

06:10.621 --> 06:12.201
<b><i>No more smoking!</i></b>

06:12.201 --> 06:14.291
<b><i>How heartless!</i></b>

06:20.051 --> 06:22.261
<b></b>Melons that
you cut for me?

06:20.051 --> 06:22.261
<b></b>I'd eat them every day!

06:20.051 --> 06:22.261
<b>badump</b>

06:30.101 --> 06:34.351
<b><i>I didn't think the web of melons 
would come into play here.</i></b>

06:34.351 --> 06:36.521
<b><i>I can't wait for the next volume.</i></b>

06:36.521 --> 06:39.271
<b>Return to Library</b>

06:36.521 --> 06:39.651
<b>Search Store</b>

06:36.521 --> 06:39.651
<b>Share</b>

06:36.521 --> 06:39.651
<b>Catch Me at the Melon Farm 4</b>

06:36.811 --> 06:40.731
<b><i>Okay, what do I read next?</i></b>

06:39.271 --> 06:39.651
<b>Return to Library</b>

06:39.441 --> 06:41.531
<b>Library</b>

06:39.441 --> 06:41.531
<b>Catch Me at
the Melon Farm</b>

06:39.441 --> 06:41.531
<b>Nishizono Hanako</b>

06:47.741 --> 06:49.581
<b>What's up, Yamada?</b>

06:49.581 --> 06:51.291
<b>Heya.</b>

06:51.291 --> 06:54.161
<b>Aren't you only on 
for the night shift today?</b>

06:54.161 --> 06:57.421
<b>Chief Maezono seemed to be having 
a hard time filling shifts,</b>

06:57.421 --> 06:58.961
<b>so I showed up anyway.</b>

07:00.341 --> 07:02.711
<b>You'd better have clocked in.</b>

07:02.711 --> 07:05.051
<b>I did. I totally did.</b>

07:05.051 --> 07:07.801
<b>Okay, good. Attagirl.</b>

07:07.801 --> 07:12.811
<b>Heck, boss. You really stopped 
smoking cigarettes, huh?</b>

07:13.181 --> 07:14.181
<b>Hmm?</b>

07:17.561 --> 07:22.981
<b>Oh, you have way more rights with these.</b>

07:22.981 --> 07:26.071
<b>And I can't be bothered 
brushing and using deodorizers.</b>

07:28.031 --> 07:30.701
<b>You're the one who taught me to, though.</b>

07:34.371 --> 07:38.001
<b>Okay, so what're you beating 
around the bush for?</b>

07:38.001 --> 07:40.671
<b>If you've got a question, 
spit it out already.</b>

07:40.581 --> 07:41.341
<b>Yamad'oh</b>

07:42.501 --> 07:47.221
<b>It's just, you haven't told me 
if the smoking is okay yet.</b>

07:47.221 --> 07:51.851
<b>What? Oh, you mean the deal 
with the gaffer.</b>

07:52.181 --> 07:57.021
<b>Maybe you didn't call the cops 
but just disposed of him instead.</b>

07:57.021 --> 07:58.851
<b>You didn't bury him 
behind the store, did you?</b>

07:58.851 --> 08:01.731
<b><i>Where do you wanna be shot?
What'll it be?</i></b>

08:01.731 --> 08:05.111
<b><i>A-Anywhere but the lungs, please!</i></b>

08:05.111 --> 08:07.111
<b>Like heck I did!</b>

08:07.111 --> 08:09.321
<b>It went in one of your ears 
and out the other,</b>

08:09.321 --> 08:12.371
<b>but I said "don't mess with him <i>too much</i>."</b>

08:12.371 --> 08:15.371
<b>In other words, just keep it low-key.</b>

08:15.661 --> 08:19.791
<b>I'm willing to overlook it because it 
won't affect anybody's work at that hour.</b>

08:19.791 --> 08:22.791
<b>If I think it's gone past low-key, 
I'll put a stop to it.</b>

08:23.881 --> 08:27.381
<b>But otherwise, it's fine. 
There you have it.</b>

08:29.171 --> 08:30.841
<b>Lucky me!</b>

08:31.591 --> 08:32.761
<b>Hey, Yamada.</b>

08:35.391 --> 08:38.141
<b>You'd better tell me ASAP 
if anything happens.</b>

08:39.231 --> 08:43.401
<b>Okay, but what do you mean by anything?</b>

08:43.691 --> 08:45.571
<b>Isn't that obvious?</b>

08:45.571 --> 08:49.651
<b>Anything that gets 
the heart racing, of course.</b>

08:51.911 --> 08:54.871
<b>Okay. Be seeing ya.</b>

09:01.371 --> 09:05.171
<b><i>Maybe I should go in and apologize.</i></b>

09:06.041 --> 09:08.341
<b>All I wanted was to show my appreciation.</b>

09:08.341 --> 09:11.171
<b>Why'd I have to go and cause 
problems for her instead?</b>

09:11.171 --> 09:12.051
<b>Hey, trespasser.</b>

09:12.051 --> 09:14.681
<b>Whoa! Please forgive me!</b>

09:15.761 --> 09:17.431
<b>Wait, Tayama-san?</b>

09:17.431 --> 09:20.181
<b>What are you sneaking 
around for, Sasaki-san?</b>

09:21.061 --> 09:25.111
<b>I ran into another employee here 
the other night.</b>

09:25.111 --> 09:27.441
<b>Did you get in trouble because of me?</b>

09:27.441 --> 09:29.691
<b>Oh, that was the manager.</b>

09:29.691 --> 09:31.951
<b>The... The manager?!</b>

09:32.741 --> 09:37.031
<b>It was fine. Anyway, come on over here.</b>

09:37.031 --> 09:38.951
<b>Wait, what?</b>

09:38.951 --> 09:42.711
<b>D-Did your manager say 
I was allowed to smoke here?</b>

09:42.711 --> 09:45.711
<b>She said to keep it low-key, 
so it's all good.</b>

09:45.711 --> 09:47.341
<b>Low-key?</b>

09:47.881 --> 09:50.711
<b><i>Is that okay or not?</i></b>

10:08.861 --> 10:10.731
<b>Also, Sasaki-san.</b>

10:12.741 --> 10:15.071
<b>This is really cute.</b>

10:17.241 --> 10:21.331
<b>I figured you didn't want reimbursement, 
but I did want to give my thanks.</b>

10:21.751 --> 10:24.001
<b>I'm glad you like it.</b>

10:24.001 --> 10:24.871
<b>I do.</b>

10:28.381 --> 10:32.261
<b>Looking at this thing makes me smile.</b>

10:32.261 --> 10:34.261
<b>Does it, now?</b>

10:34.261 --> 10:38.051
<b>Because I can picture you 
picking it out at the store.</b>

10:39.891 --> 10:43.311
<b>Wait, why would that make you smile?</b>

10:43.311 --> 10:46.811
<b>I mean, it can't have been 
easy to find this thing.</b>

10:46.811 --> 10:50.021
<b>They don't sell a lot of 
cute ashtrays like it.</b>

10:57.531 --> 11:01.621
<b>I can imagine you had to ask people 
where they were selling these,</b>

11:02.291 --> 11:05.291
<b>and because the trinket sections 
are always full of women,</b>

11:05.291 --> 11:10.961
<b>you would've felt all awkward as you 
stood there picking a good one out.</b>

11:15.051 --> 11:18.091
<b>Tayama-san, you really can 
read minds, can't you?</b>

11:25.101 --> 11:30.061
<b>Anyway, picturing all that 
puts a smile on my face.</b>

11:31.231 --> 11:34.691
<b>Are you sure you don't just see 
this geezer as entertainment?</b>

11:34.691 --> 11:38.571
<b>What? I don't. It genuinely 
makes me feel better.</b>

11:39.361 --> 11:42.331
<b><i>I can never tell if she's 
being serious or not.</i></b>

11:51.381 --> 11:52.591
<b>Thanks.</b>

11:53.671 --> 11:54.881
<b>I'll cherish it.</b>

11:58.431 --> 12:01.341
<b><i>I guess it's fine either way.</i></b>

12:01.341 --> 12:03.051
<b>Hey, Sasaki-san.</b>

12:03.851 --> 12:06.351
<b>You should probably ash that.</b>

12:07.351 --> 12:09.101
<b>Oh, you're right.</b>

12:09.731 --> 12:11.611
<b>Go ahead and use this.</b>

12:12.361 --> 12:16.151
<b>Sure is handy, huh? Thanks...</b>

12:18.401 --> 12:20.111
<b><i>Th-That's kind of close.</i></b>

12:20.491 --> 12:23.121
<b>We don't want you getting a burn.</b>

12:23.831 --> 12:24.871
<b>So here.</b>

12:25.581 --> 12:26.501
<b>Come on.</b>

12:26.871 --> 12:28.911
<b>U-Uh...</b>

12:28.911 --> 12:32.131
<b>C-Can you just hand it to me?</b>

12:32.131 --> 12:34.501
<b>Okay, go ahead and take it.</b>

12:36.381 --> 12:37.671
<b>What...</b>

12:38.131 --> 12:40.801
<b>A bit more. Almost there.</b>

12:45.601 --> 12:46.891
<b>Tayama-san...</b>

12:47.391 --> 12:49.681
<b>Why are you moving it away?</b>

12:49.681 --> 12:52.151
<b>Oh, sorry about that.</b>

12:52.941 --> 12:55.521
<b>Sasaki-san, you've got some long arms.</b>

12:55.521 --> 12:57.651
<b>Give it to me, Tayama-san.</b>

12:57.651 --> 13:00.651
<b>Before my arm gives out.</b>

13:03.161 --> 13:06.581
<b>Ow... Ouch!</b>

13:06.581 --> 13:07.331
<b>Huh?</b>

13:13.251 --> 13:14.671
<b><i>A compress?</i></b>

13:15.501 --> 13:16.921
<b><i>Don't tell me...</i></b>

13:20.091 --> 13:21.301
<b>Are you okay?</b>

13:21.301 --> 13:25.801
<b>I'm fine. I just choked a little.</b>

13:25.801 --> 13:29.221
<b>I'm really sorry, okay?</b>

13:29.221 --> 13:32.941
<b>You don't have to apologize, Yamada-san.</b>

13:33.271 --> 13:37.111
<b><i>Old man cramps last for days, huh?</i></b>

13:38.401 --> 13:40.941
<b>Forgive me, Sasaki-san.</b>

13:41.361 --> 13:42.821
<b>I-It's okay!</b>

13:43.321 --> 13:45.071
<b>It's all right, Yamada-san!</b>

13:45.071 --> 13:45.991
<b>I'm so sorry.</b>

13:45.991 --> 13:47.911
<b>Don't be! Please don't be!</b>

13:47.911 --> 13:50.581
<b>Please stop apologizing!</b>

13:48.951 --> 13:51.331
<b>No, I must apologize.</b>

13:50.581 --> 13:52.961
<b>You haven't done anything wrong!</b>

13:53.201 --> 13:56.831
<b>Translation: Sriram Gurunathan</b>

13:57.331 --> 14:00.961
<b>Editing & Typesetting: Geoff Mazzolini
Subtitle Timing: Krzysztof Kunc</b>

14:01.671 --> 14:04.921
<b>Quality Check: Zachary Carlysle
Translation Check: Sho Stifler</b>
